{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"eaa988eed8","title":"关于乔冠华、黄华等回京参加日内瓦会议筹备工作的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b189a1ceeb","index":0,"year":1954,"month":3,"day":1,"articleId":"eaa988eed8"}],"tags":[{"id":"8bb2374059","name":"杜平","type":"人物"},{"id":"97df5c1988","name":"丁国钰","type":"人物"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e383c6d737","name":"乔冠华","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"80d4f66a9f","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"乔冠华、黄华，当时均任朝鲜停战谈判中国人民志愿军代表团党委委员。"},{"id":"2dd7e79f79","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"杜平，当时任中国人民志愿军政治部主任、朝鲜停战谈判朝中代表团代表、中国人民志愿军代表团党委副书记。"},{"id":"98513b4748","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"金首相，指朝鲜民主主义人民共和国首相金日成。彭司令员，指中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀。"},{"id":"23d67027fd","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李克农，当时任中央人民政府外交部副部长、中国人民解放军副总参谋长、朝鲜停战谈判中国人民志愿军代表团党委书记，负责主持朝鲜停战谈判朝中代表团的工作。"},{"id":"5c3ae66477","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"丁国钰，当时任朝鲜停战谈判朝中代表团代表、中国人民志愿军代表团党委委员。"},{"id":"be8e395dd4","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李相朝，朝鲜人民军中将，当时任朝鲜停战谈判朝中代表团首席代表。"},{"id":"c9b14d420b","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","index":7,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柴成文，当时任朝鲜停战谈判中国人民志愿军代表团党委委员、秘书长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0924cdec60","type":"title","text":"关于乔冠华、黄华等回京参加日内瓦会议筹备工作的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"80d4f66a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"杜平回、乔冠华同志，并告金首相、彭司令员以：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"2dd7e79f79","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿八日电悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"98513b4748","type":"paragraph","text":"一、为了准备参加日内瓦会议，同意季克农同志意见，乔冠华、黄华等同志迅速回京，参加筹备工作。乔、黄过平时应向金首相报告工作并请示意见","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"23d67027fd","type":"paragraph","text":"二、同意代表团党委改组，由丁国钰同志任党委副书记；以后向北京、平的报告请示改由李相朝、杜平、丁国钰三同志","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"5c3ae66477","type":"subtitle","text":"署名。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"be8e395dd4","type":"paragraph","text":"三、因杜平同志尚不能完全离开部队工作，故在杜不在开城时，党委工作即由丁国钰同志负责（柴成文同志协助），向北京、平的报告请示即由李相朝、丁国钰二同志署名。在工作情况许可的条件下，丁国钰、柴成文二同志可以轮流回国休假。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"c9b14d420b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"},{"id":"88cc6f0123","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年三月一日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8"}],"page":{"id":"4e88597f53","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eaa988eed8","start":38,"end":39}}}},"__N_SSG":true}